---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="TELOS | Problems Missions Goals and Life Direction" description="Personal framework for tracking purpose and direction in life">
  <main class="relative z-10 pt-28 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">TELOS Framework</h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-secondary">
          A structured approach to understanding problems, defining missions, setting goals, and measuring progress.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problems -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent bg-accent/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">P</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Problems</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          The fundamental issues I see in the world that need addressing.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Privacy as Autonomy</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• The average person cannot control what they share about themselves</li>
                  <li>• Privacy isn't about hiding — it's about the right to reveal exactly and only what you choose</li>
                  <li>• This control is currently available only to those with technical knowledge or money</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">AI Democratization</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Human-AI convergence is happening, but access is stratified</li>
                  <li>• AI should not be a tool only for elites</li>
                  <li>• The technology that could level playing fields is instead deepening divides</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P3</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Autonomy is Gatekept</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Both P1 and P2 are faces of the same issue</li>
                  <li>• Wealth and technical knowledge determine who gets self-determination</li>
                  <li>• I'm working on both fronts to change this</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Missions -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand bg-brand/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">M</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Missions</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          My response to these problems through focused action.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Build Open Infrastructure for Personal Data Sovereignty</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Build tools — all MIT licensed — that let people own their data</li>
                  <li>• Own their AI relationships and take their context with them</li>
                  <li>• Not depend on companies that monetize them or institutions that revoke access</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Bridge Security and AI</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Leverage 20 years of Information Security expertise</li>
                  <li>• Ensure AI is deployed safely and accessibly</li>
                  <li>• Bring security-first thinking to a field moving faster than it understands</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M3</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Share Knowledge Openly</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Build in public, share what works</li>
                  <li>• Everything open source, everything MIT licensed</li>
                  <li>• Because this shouldn't be just for elites</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Goals -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success bg-success/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">G</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Goals</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          Specific, measurable outcomes I'm working toward.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Sovereign Infrastructure</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Self-hosted, privacy-first, local-first systems</li>
                  <li>• No dependency on cloud providers or platforms</li>
                  <li>• Infrastructure that can't be taken away</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">AI Partnership Tools</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Memory systems and persona generators</li>
                  <li>• Frameworks that let people own their AI relationships</li>
                  <li>• Not renting capability from corporations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G3</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Privacy-First Applications</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <li>• Tools for selective sharing</li>
                  <li>• Share what you want, when you want, with whom you want</li>
                  <li>• And nothing more</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Metrics -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary mb-6">Metrics (KPIs)</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand mb-2">Sovereignty</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Tools deployed, data owned locally, dependencies eliminated</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand mb-2">Adoption</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Open source downloads, forks, community contributions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand mb-2">Learning</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Build cycles completed, lessons documented, skills acquired</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand mb-2">Impact</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">People helped, autonomy enabled, gatekeeping reduced</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <section class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-8">
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-tertiary italic">
          TELOS is a living framework that evolves as I learn and grow. The north star stays fixed: build tools that give people sovereignty over their own lives. Theme: "The context you keep."
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
